title: All2MP3 Converter Mac *Latest Update*
description:
All2MP3 is an application for mac that converts APE, MPC, FLAC, WV, OGG, WMA, AIFF, WAV & MORE to MP3 files in the quality of your choice (Less being 160 kbps and super being 320 kbps and joint stereo)

 -Version 2.0820 Works on latest OS at this time Mavericks.


*I'd highly recommend this for those odd file types you come across when you can't find your music as an mp3 and want the best possible conversion. 

Of course From flac to mp3 320 would be the best possible conversion to mp3 as far as I know. 

It's good for knowing you're getting the best quality conversions of listening to your music besides flac which you could do with VLC media player.*
